We were received with open arms.

00:29:03.460 --> 00:29:05.820 align:middle line:84%
But the question is
could we get an interview

00:29:05.820 --> 00:29:06.960 align:middle line:90%
with the Shankaracharya.

00:29:06.960 --> 00:29:08.360 align:middle line:84%
It's like getting an
interview with the pope.

00:29:08.360 --> 00:29:09.610 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: With the pope, yeah.

00:29:09.610 --> 00:29:11.220 align:middle line:84%
>>DAVIDS: And we're
waiting day by day

00:29:11.220 --> 00:29:13.740 align:middle line:90%
to see can we get an interview.

