And I have a fellow
producer who I

00:29:16.980 --> 00:29:22.030 align:middle line:84%
invited into the project
who's from India, Anil Urmil.

00:29:22.030 --> 00:29:24.270 align:middle line:84%
And he had some
family connections

00:29:24.270 --> 00:29:27.940 align:middle line:84%
and he was-- he
