00:29:40.100 --> 00:29:40.970 align:middle line:90%
with him to prove.

00:29:40.970 --> 00:29:42.240 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: He didn't know
you had the force with you.

00:29:42.240 --> 00:29:43.073 align:middle line:90%
>>DAVIDS: He didn't.

00:29:43.073 --> 00:29:44.150 align:middle line:90%
He didn't know.

00:29:44.150 --> 00:29:45.890 align:middle line:90%
None of us knew that.

00:29:45.890 --> 00:29:48.600 align:middle line:84%
Because when we got
there-- well, what he said

00:29:48.600 --> 00:29:51.050 align:middle line:84%
is there's an American
filmmaker here.

00:29:51.050 --> 00:29:54.590 align:middle line:84%
And he loves
Paramahansa Yogananda

00:29:54.590 --> 00:29:55.790 align:middle line:90%
and the Shankaracharya.

00:29:55.790 --> 00:29:59.780 align:middle line:84%
He said oh, then
this Paul Davids, I

00:29:59.780 --> 00:30:02.460 align:middle line:84%
must consider him
an honorary Hindu.

00:30:02.460 --> 00:30:04.265 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Interesting OK.

00:30:04.265 --> 00:30:05.140 align:middle line:90%
>>DAVIDS: Come, come.

00:30:05.140 --> 00:30:05.410 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: That's how it--

00:30:05.410 --> 00:30:06.820 align:middle line:90%
>>DAVIDS: You have a camera.

00:30:06.820 --> 00:30:08.310 align:middle line:90%
Let's talk about Jesus in India.

00:30:08.310 --> 00:30:09.800 align:middle line:90%
I will tell you.

00:30:09.800 --> 00:30:15.790 align:middle line:84%
So we go into this room and
