00:30:15.790 --> 00:30:20.340 align:middle line:84%
There are four
Shankaracharyas in Hinduism.

00:30:20.340 --> 00:30:24.730 align:middle line:84%
But the one we met with is
like the leader of them all.

00:30:24.730 --> 00:30:27.580 align:middle line:84%
So this was like a
meeting with the pope.

00:30:27.580 --> 00:30:30.690 align:middle line:84%
And I don't know
